TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message (Persistent)
TriggerLogic.Message: We must set up a mining operation on this asteroid. However, the enemy is already here.

TriggerLogic.Name: Add Objective
TriggerLogic.Description: Destroy all six mexes around your position.
TriggerLogic.Title: Destroy Mexes

TriggerLogic.Message: Good work, now get your own mining operations underway. To get into the core of this asteroid, we'll need a Planetary Energy Chisel.
- Use a Planetary Energy Chisel to destroy the enemy reactor.

TriggerLogic.Description: Use the Starlight Planetary Energy Chisel to destroy the enemy reactor from a safe distance. Don't even think about attacking it directly, it's not going to work.
TriggerLogic.Title: Destroy Reactor
